;; tokens.aski — token classification
;; Maps Token enum variants to their grammatical roles.

Delimiter (LParen RParen LBracket RBracket LBrace RBrace)
Operator (Plus Minus Star Slash Percent DoubleEquals NotEqual LessThan GreaterThan LessThanOrEqual GreaterThanOrEqual LogicalAnd LogicalOr)
Prefix (Caret Hash Bang At Colon Tilde)
Compound (CompositionOpen CompositionClose TraitBoundOpen TraitBoundClose IterOpen IterClose)
